data.description: **5.75% interest rate ASSUMABLE LOAN for VA buyers!!  LOCATION! LOCATION! Come be a part of all the fun! Newly renovated 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 1 car garage home minutes away from downtown, 1 mile from Tyrone Mall, and 5 miles from ST. PETE beautiful beaches. As you step inside, you’ll be greeted with an amazing open floor plan, with luxury vinyl flooring, and modern style feel. The luxury eat-in kitchen features a beautiful waterfall island complemented with granite countertops, upgraded soft-close cabinetry and elegant backsplash. This split floor plan offers 2 spacious secondary bedrooms and a fully updated bathroom. The Master Suite features a walk-in closet, with a floor to ceiling tiled inlayed shower. On the rear of the home, you will find a large Florida Bonus room, with beautiful natural lighting that can be used as an office, game room, or dining room. Spacious backyard with plenty of room to expand your outdoor entertainment, which also features newly installed vinyl fencing, shed for extra storage, and room for all your toys (RV, boat, etc.) This home features a tile roof with newly installed solar panels, new AC, and updated light fixtures throughout the property. NO HOA, NO CDD, NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE! Must come and see! Private showings available!
